title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 24 2022
description:
RT reports Moscow is willing to negotiate terms of surrender in exchange for Ukraine guarantee of neutral status and the promise of no weapons on its territory. Clay and Buck preview Biden's speech. Never forget what tyrant Trudeau did to the truckers. C&B join President Biden's speech in progress, in order to provide their insightful analysis.
